{"word":"Bereavement","slug":"bereavement","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bereavement</b> From God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=29'>Exo 12:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=9&verse=12'>Hos 9:12</a><br/> Mourning in, forbidden to Aaron, on account of his son's wickedness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=6'>Lev 10:6</a><br/> Mourning in, forbidden to Ezekiel, for his wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=24&verse=18'>Eze 24:18</a><br/> Instances of:<br/> - Abraham, of Sarah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=23&verse=2'>Gen 23:2</a> <br/> - Jacob, of Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=35'>Gen 37:35</a> <br/> - Joseph, of his father<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=1'>Gen 50:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=4'>Gen 50:4</a> <br/> - The Egyptians, of their firstborn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=33'>Exo 12:33</a> <br/> - Naomi, of her husband<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=3'>Rth 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=5'>Rth 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=21'>Rth 1:21</a> <br/> - David, of his child by Bath-Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=23'>2Sa 12:23</a> <br/> - Absalom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=33'>2Sa 18:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=4'>2Sa 19:4</a> <br/> Resignation in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=23'>2Sa 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=1&verse=21'>Job 1:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=7&verse=4'>Ecc 7:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=4&verse=18'>1Th 4:18</a><br/><a href='S:Afflictions, Consolation in'>Afflictions, Consolation in</a>; <a href='S:Afflictions, Resignation in'>Afflictions, Resignation in</a>; <a href='S:Resignation'>Resignation</a>"}]}